Installing current version of git:

since these scripts are doing a checkout of a git repository, you need to have git and git-lfs installed on your system.

Install git with conda:

conda create git python=3.12
conda activate git
conda install -c conda-forge git git-lfs
git lfs install

Add to path:
~/.conda/envs/git/bin:

Check with:
git --version
git lfs env